Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE DARK HYUNCKEL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They kept them tied up there all night?\NThey're inhumane!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Crocodine, we'll get you out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,at its zenith, shining at its brightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:02:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It is noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru, are those\Nall of the enemy's forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shadow Legion Commander\Nand armoured monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's 36 of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense a great amount of pressure\Ncoming from Ban Palace...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's all for the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be able to handle\Nsuch a number...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,excluding Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, I'm sure you haven't forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you drink the Dark Aura in\Nthis chalice and serve me or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want an answer, then free me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:04:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, once you drink this it is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You will have sold\Nyour soul to the devil again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.09,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,don't forget... what I told you... please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you thought you'd pretend\Nto submit as a way to trick me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, my Dark Aura is\Nnot so easily overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you intended,\Nyou belong to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!\NWhat happened to Sir Hyunckel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He drank from that strange cup\Nand completely changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Dark Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense an evil presence from Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's likely being affected\Nby the enemy's Dark Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He accepted an evil influence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How could a Disciple of Aban do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If told to behead someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you feel you could do it easily,\Nas if picking a flower, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,At last you are back where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous! He wouldn't lose\Nhis righteous heart so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Limited as it is, you have\Nthe ability to manipulate Aura, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at him, don't you sense it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't sense his Aura of Light!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's completely enveloped in Dark Aura!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}E-Even now, the last of Hyunckel's\NAura of Light is being consumed!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears he underestimated my Dark Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:07:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He assumed if he pretended to submit\Nand accepted my Aura,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,then he could overcome it\Nwith his own Aura of Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some things in this world\Nthat cannot be overcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of darkness has no limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, it appears your final gambit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,has ended in failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You still seem sluggish, Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of darkness\Nhas healed your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The sluggishness is because\Nyou still retain a shred of conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you how to become\Na complete warrior again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this and execute Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing a former friend\Nwill extinguish your conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll lose your Aura of Light and again\Nbecome a true Dark Swordsman of Evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You can't go out there yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hyunckel is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not supposed to charge\Nuntil Dai and the others rescue those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't rescue them like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What can I do?!\NHyunckel is now an enemy!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you consider me a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:09:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to trust me no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right! He's still fighting!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a desperate battle\Nraging inside of him!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to believe in him!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let the Dark Aura take you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Kill!\NKill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm cut to shreds,\NI'll believe in you to the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So fight! Fight that evil within you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him, Hyunckel!\NDon't listen to his nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's... dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If he had just accepted it,\Nhe could have returned to the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't endure the conflicting Auras\Nand it killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel's life energy has disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we can no longer gather\Nfive Disciples of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:11:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Dai doing?!\NI've waited long enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason they haven't appeared\Nis because they understand Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Life itself is but\None more weapon for him to wield.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Disappointing, but so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me give you a companion\Nto take to the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel really good, Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now I feel like\NI could behead you easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,As if...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,picking a flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:07.53,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BLOODY SUKURAIDO!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:12.54,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}TOMAKUGUTSOSHO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! I'm sure I felt\Nyour life energy vanish!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Two opposing Auras\Nwere battling inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,one of them won!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What you felt was the Aura that lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:13:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this possible?!\NWhy is your Aura of Light so powerful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that my Aura of Light\Nwas suppressed by your Dark Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Overwhelmed by your evil power,\Nit was almost extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But, as a result,\Nmy Aura of Light grew stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My will not to give in to evil\Nmade my Aura of Light even more powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And in turn, it suppressed your Dark Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!\NThat was your intent from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You used my Dark Aura to\Nhelp boost your own power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You once told me that abandoning\Nmy Aura of darkness had made me weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't because I couldn't use\Nboth opposing powers at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When evil, I hated the power of light\Nthat Aban had bestowed upon me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When good, I sought to overcome\Nthe power of darkness within me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This rapidly boosted both Auras!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you told me to accept your dark power{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I took it as a final chance\Nto shine even brighter than before!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying your Aura of Light\Nhas actually suppressed my Dark Aura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you could do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you already sense it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Aura within me that has been\Ncompletely enveloped by my Aura of Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking out Restless Armours bare-handed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the power of Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,His overflowing Aura\Nhas made his body harder than steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he's powered up\Nbeyond imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew that was\NHyunckel's plan all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a risky gamble,\Nbut fortunately it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who's they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you...\NMy face shall not be touched!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, you're always\Npushing yourself to the extreme!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you intend to make up\Nfor scaring me half to death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:16:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine, I'll take care of these guys\Nand get you out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to tear both of you apart\Nhere and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Both of you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban, it looks like your senses dull\Nwhen you get emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,D-...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So he still lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My fortune telling has never missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense spirit within him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Like he's a whole different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Renewed your resolve?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Popp! Maam! And even Princess Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We tunneled in like you do, Big Guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to use\Nmy fire magic instead, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me get those!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, I'm surprised\Nyou didn't jump the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I sensed the Aura of Light inside you\Ngrowing stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We were worried at first, but we quickly\Nswitched to an attack from underground!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You believed in me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't only Dai who\Nbelieved in you, Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to charge the moment\Nyou went all dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But she stopped us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel would never accept Dark Aura\Nif he didn't know he could beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's trust him and see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I made a vow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd only ever fight with\Nthe power of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them can still fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nova!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We've run out of patience, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's set to explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's game time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.02,0:19:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use them to blow off some steam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, why are you\Nleaving the fighting to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's all a little complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, do you still have\Nyour Insignia of Aban?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They could kill me\Nand I wouldn't let go of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it in your hand\Nand focus your will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus... my will?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not anything difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just focus your thoughts\Non what gives you the will to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm just the worst!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For a moment I actually hoped\Nthat Hyunckel's Insignia wouldn't glow.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That if Hyunckel couldn't do it,\Nit'd let me off the hook.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! The Insignia of Aban is glowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Insignia must be responding\Nto your fortitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all set now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We have five Disciples and five Insignias!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Purification Spell\NMinakator is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you Dai! Curse you Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've humiliated me time and time again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong, Mystban?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dark King!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so agitated?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,With your power you could\Nwipe out all of them easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as though their resistance\Nwill gain them entry into Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your time and show\Nthose who would resist me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,what true suffering really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, my King! Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As you command, I shall offer you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the sight of them writhing in agony!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall tear you all apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.34,0:21:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Dark Puppetry Aura Decimation Field!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got... other things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have time for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to play...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.94,0:21:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'll play with you, Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:12.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:18.37,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.87,0:22:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.87,0:22:23.84,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:29.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:35.60,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:41.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:47.36,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.53,0:22:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.53,0:22:53.37,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:59.16,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.33,0:23:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.33,0:23:01.79,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.96,0:23:05.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.96,0:23:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.25,0:23:10.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.25,0:23:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:16.64,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:22.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:25.27,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:30.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.59,0:23:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The five Disciples of Aban gather at last.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ritual of Minakator begins,\Nwith Leona at its center.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mystban tries to stop the spell,\Nbut Ron Berku thwarts him.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.56,0:23:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crocodine and the others fight to protect\Nthe five Disciples from the Dark Army.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With everyone counting on them,\Nwill the Great Purification Spell succeed?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.86,0:23:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.24,0:23:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Five Colors of Light"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.95,0:24:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.06,0:24:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,
